------------------------------------------------------------------------
2008-12-29 13:56  ahuillet  r1406
   M /dialogs/Butch.dialog
   M /dialogs/Dixon.dialog
   M /dialogs/KevinGuard.dialog
   M /dialogs/MSFacilityGateGuardLeader.dialog
   M /dialogs/Michelangelo.dialog
   M /dialogs/SACD.dialog
   M /dialogs/SADD.dialog
   M /dialogs/Spencer.dialog
   M /dialogs/Tybalt.dialog
   M /dialogs/subdlg_Butch.dialog
   M /dialogs/subdlg_Duncan.dialog
   M /dialogs/subdlg_Kevin.dialog
   M /map/freedroid.events
   M /map/freedroid.quests
   M /src/Makefile.am
   M /src/chat.c
   M /src/defs.h
   M /src/event.c
   M /src/global.h
   M /src/init.c
   M /src/menu.c
   M /src/mission.c
   M /src/proto.h
   M /src/saveloadgame.c
   M /src/savestruct.c
   M /src/struct.h
   M /src/text_public.c

Integrated Lua into the game to implement event actions in a simpler and more powerful manner.
Event triggers now directly specify a piece of Lua code to execute, missions can give a lua script to be run at 
assignment or completion, and dialogs have a new LuaCode field to interact with the environment (change obstacles).



